g views from the highest peaks that you will experience. It's one of the most pristine Madikeri destinations to visit. Therefore, wildlife and environment enthusiasts must go there and Witness The Rare Birds. The address is Kodagu, Coorg, Somwarpet (571251). 18. Iruppu Falls: It is situated 50 kilometres away from Madikeri and is also known as Lakshmana Teertha Falls. The villagers think that this fall's water can wipe away sins. This is one of the key factors contributing to its increased popularity among visitors. Among the places to see in Madikeri, the breathtaking waterfall that cascades from the Coorg mountains are a spectacular sight and a tranquil atmosphere. The Address is 571250 Brahmagiri, Kurchi, Karnataka. 19. Chingara Falls: This waterfall is one of the greatest tourist destinations in Madikeri because of its position. It is one of the most picturesque locations, surrounded by coffee plantations and tropical forests, with the natural waterfall offering the perfect atmosphere. Many hikers and adventure seekers like visiting this waterfall as a favourite spot to go rock climbing and rappelling. To spend your time away from nature, you may select to stay at some of the best resorts in Madikeri. Chingara Falls is the best picnic location. The address is Kabbinakad, Madikeri Taluk, Coorg District, Yavakapadi Village Post, Karnataka 571212. 20. Harangi Backwaters: The journey to the backwaters is quite dangerous but well worth it because they are undoubtedly some of the most beautiful. You will be rewarded with stunning scenery that will completely surprise you after hiking through lush jungles. Watch a spectacular sunset over the pristine backwaters, surrounded by lush greenery and stunning scenery. One of the greatest places for families to go on vacation in India to take in the scenery is Karnataka. The address is Kodagu, Karnataka, 571234, Hudgur, Somwarpet, Harangi Dam. 21. St Michael's Church: A Catholic church, St. Michael's Church, is one among the many places of worship in Madikeri. Do you long for the tranquillity you expect from a vacation? Especially on a Sunday when there is prayer, there can be nothing better than going to this church. There is a lot of open space around the church and attractive contemporary architecture. You'll feel better just by being there. The address is Madikeri, Karnataka 571201, Virajpet Road, Stuart Hill. 22. Chettali: One more of the tourist destinations in Madikeri provides a purely exclusive experience. A cute little town near Madikeri that is surrounded by greenery. You will be surprised by the village's peaks, hills, and beautiful scenery when you come, just like in your art book. Remember to stop at the neighbouring waterfall and the Cherala Bhagavathy temple. If you haven't noticed, vast areas are also covered with plantations. The address is 571248 Madikeri in Karnataka. 23. Chiklihole Reservoir: To completely explore Chiklihole Reservoir, plan to stay there for at least a day. Undoubtedly, it's a popular destination for tourists in Madikeri, providing a calm environment, a lot of greenery, and a pleasant atmosphere. But instead of the normal crowds, you will enjoy the tranquillity and peace you want here. The large open areas and lush greenery attract your mind to a tranquil picnic with loved ones or even friends. Chiklihole Reservoir is located in Attur Forest, Karnataka, at address 571234. 24. Coffee Plantations: Coffee Plantations is a vast expanse, not a specific location, with lush greenery and the delightful fragrance of herbs. These are Madikeri's various coffee plantations spread across the region. The plantations are lined with many acres of greenery, little strolling paths, and pleasant moods that make your trip enjoyable. Can you think of any other Madikeri locations to visit that would provide the same outcome, Without a doubt? The address is Stuart Hill in Madikeri, Karnataka 571201. 25. Nehru Mantap: Nehru Mantap is among the less well-known attractions in Madikeri. The Madikeri Radio Station and the surrounding mountains may be seen from the mandap area, which is a pleasant sight. Nehru Mantap, near Raja's Seat, is unquestionably a day trip you should make, especially if you enjoy nature. Don't miss the stunning sunrise and sunset views. In Madikeri, Karnataka, near Stuart Hill, at 571201. Next TopicTourist Places in Malappuram ? prev next ? For Videos Join Our Youtube Channel: Join Now Feedback Send your Feedback to [email protected] Help Others, Please Share Learn Latest Tutorials Splunk SPSS Swagger Transact-SQL Tumblr ReactJS Regex Reinforcement Learning R Programming RxJS React Native Python Design Patterns Python Pillow Python Turtle Keras Preparation Aptitude Reasoning Verbal Ability Interview Questions Company Questions Trending Technologies Artificial Intelligence AWS Selenium Cloud Computing Hadoop ReactJS Data Science Angular 7 Blockchain Git Machine Learning DevOps B.Tech / MCA DBMS Data Structures DAA Operating System Computer Network Compiler Design Computer Organization Discrete Mathematics Ethical Hacking Computer Graphics Software Engineering Web Technology Cyber Security Automata C Programming C++ Java .Net Python Programs Control System Data Mining Data Warehouse Javatpoint Services JavaTpoint offers too many high quality services. Mail us on [email protected], to get more information about given services. Website Designing Website Development Java Development PHP Development WordPress Graphic Designing Logo Digital Marketing On Page and Off Page SEO PPC Content Development Corporate Training Classroom and Online Training Data Entry Training For College Campus JavaTpoint offers college campus training on Core Java, Advance Java, .Net, Android, Hadoop, PHP, Web Technology and Python. Please mail your requirement at [email protected] Duration: 1 week to 2 week Like/Subscribe us for latest updates or newsletter Learn TutorialsLearn JavaLearn Data StructuresLearn C ProgrammingLearn C++ TutorialLearn C